According to preliminary data, they confirmed that sabotage was organized by the Ukrainian intelligence services.
US authorities forced Mask to leave the post of Tesla chairman of the board
American businessman Elon Musk will leave the post of chairman of the board of directors founded by him Tesla at the request of the U.S. authorities.
