The speakers were Yuliya Dyakova, candidate of physical and mathematical sciences, head of the Kurchatov complex of the NBIKS-nature technologies of the Research Center “Kurchatov Institute” and the head of Kurchatovsky of the NBICS technology complex Vyacheslav Demin.
